caption: b'One way to make your Instagram posts more accessible is by adding alt text. This ensures that screen readers recognize your image, allowing visually impaired users to hear a description. Join us on this International Day of Persons with Disabilities by adding alt text to your posts and help make the world a little more inclusive. #IDPWD2020 #InclusionInAction'
b'Gobble up the latest, from #Thanksgiving turkey prices to #BlackFriday purchasing trends - all on the #BloombergTerminal. :turkey:'
b'Giving you a glimpse behind the scenes of @BloombergTV this #WorldTelevisionDay :television:'
b'The #BloombergTerminal never stops being useful - from keyboard to magnet. Can you guess which keyboard model these are from? #BeRecycled'
b"Follow the latest news, videos, polls, and tweets on this year's general #election with ELEC <GO> on the #BloombergTerminal."
b"It's spooky how our Bloomberg Intelligence team always has the latest research on market-moving events! BI <GO> is full of treats on the #BloombergTerminal. :ghost:"
b'Bringing transparency to data in everything that we do. Check out STAT <GO> on the #BloombergTerminal. #WorldStatisticsDay'
b"Go ahead - delve into our world of data. It's a piece of cake. :shortcake: #NationalDessertDay"
b"Can you tell we love the #BloombergTerminal 'a latte'? :hot_beverage:"

b'When your product sits on the desks of some of the world\xe2\x80\x99s most influential decision makers, the computing infrastructure behind it must work flawlessly. This #TechiesDay, join us in celebrating our technologists who help make it possible.'

b"You've watched us on TV and read us on the web, but have you listened to our podcasts? Hear them all - on and off the #BloombergTerminal at BPOD <GO>, Apple Podcasts, Google Podcasts, and Spotify. #InternationalPodcastDay"
b'The seasons may change, but the #BloombergTerminal will never leaf you. Happy #FirstDayofFall.'
b'Leveling up since 1981 \xe2\x80\x94 no matter where we are. #BloombergTerminal #NationalVideoGamesDay :video_game:'
b'Giving our appreciation this #LaborDay to our colleagues, who have been working hard, working responsibly, doing whatever it takes to keep you keeping on. #workonpurpose'
b'Getting you the information you need...when you need it the most. #workonpurpose'
b"When your pup hops on the #BloombergTerminal, it's hard not to have a paw-sitive outlook. Happy #NationalDogDay :dog_face:\n:camera_with_flash: credit: @mollythedoodlebear"
b"Wherever you crunch the numbers, we're right there with you. #BloombergTerminal"

b'With the launch of our proprietary ESG scores, investors can now quickly evaluate performance across a range of key issues, such as climate change or health and safety. View the scores at BI ESG <GO> on your #BloombergTerminal'
b"Looking for some last-minute summer reading? Here are some books that we think are the cat's meow. #InternationalCatDay #BookLoversDay :cat_face: :open_book:"
b'The global economy never sleeps, so you need a partner who can keep up no matter what. At Bloomberg, we keep on, so you can keep on.'
b'This #WorldEmojiDay, we celebrate a day in the world of finance - emoji style. #BloombergTerminal'

b'Riding into the long weekend in style. :bicycle:'

b"Whether you're out for a (socially-distanced) walk or on your couch, we work hard to get the data in your hands with the Bloomberg Professional app."

b'With {MAP FISH <GO>} on the #BloombergTerminal, you can access Global Fishing Watch\xe2\x80\x99s data and geospatial tools, which we hope will increase monitoring and protection of ocean ecosystems and communities at risk from overfishing and climate change. #WorldOceansDay :fish::blowfish::shark::tropical_fish:'
b"The word 'parent' has a different meaning this year. On this @UnitedNations #GlobalDayofParents, join us in celebrating all the hardworking #BloombergTerminal parents around the world."

b"This #ScavengerHuntDay, we're taking you on a digital trip down memory lane. Here are four closeup clues to some of our favorite past Instagram shots. Double tap once you find them on our page, and let us know in the comments below when you've found all four!"
b'In a time where every day is #WorkFromHomeDay, be sure to take time to focus on yourself and your mental health.  #MentalHealthAwarenessMonth'
b'#MayThe4th screen be with you, even in the comfort of your own home.'
b'A #BloombergTerminal user in the making. \nThis #BabyDay, show us your future Terminal users.'

b"Over the years, we've seen #BloombergTerminal cakes, gingerbread houses and even ones made of LEGO. This #NationalLookAlikeDay, check out our Instagram Story for a brand new lookalike - the official Bloomberg Terminal coloring book. :camera_with_flash: credits: @denisemakescakes @issofine @pcwilliams"
b'Working from home is ten times better when you get to do it with a #BloombergTerminal and a bearded dragon named Tulip. #NationalPetDay'
b"#AprilShowers might bring May flowers that feel quite far from reach, but we're ready for some fresh air when the time is right. :umbrella_with_rain_drops:"

b'Companies with trans-inclusive policies have more equitable corporate cultures, enabling employees to thrive. The LGBTQ100 ESG Index tracks U.S. companies that are most committed to supporting equality for the LGBTQ+ community - and has outperformed the S&P 500 for the last five years. LGBTQ100 Index DES <GO> on the #BloombergTerminal. #TDoV'
